sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Player as Browser Player
  participant Client as @phalanxduel/client
  participant Server as Fastify WS/App
  participant Shared as @phalanxduel/shared
  participant Engine as @phalanxduel/engine

  rect rgb(245, 248, 255)
    Note over Client,Server: Liveness and session recovery
    Client->>Server: ping / pong heartbeat + native WS keepalive
    alt socket silently drops or heartbeat times out
      Client->>Client: Mark CONNECTING and schedule reconnect with backoff + jitter
      Client->>Server: rejoinMatch(matchId, playerId, msgId)
      Server-->>Client: ack + matchJoined
      Client->>Server: Replay pending reliable messages by msgId
      Server-->>Client: ack or cached response replay
    end
  end

  Player->>Client: Choose move in match UI
  Client->>Server: WS action + msgId + telemetry envelope
  Server-->>Client: ack(ackedMsgId)
  Server->>Shared: Parse and validate action schema
  Server->>Engine: applyAction(current GameState, Action)
  Engine-->>Server: PhalanxTurnResult + PhalanxEvent[]
  Server->>Shared: Compute hashes and serialize view model
  Server-->>Client: Broadcast gameState + turn result
  Client-->>Player: Render updated battlefield, phase, and log cues
